  <section>
    <h2 id="product-reviews">Product reviews by use-case</h2>
    <p><strong>How we evaluate:</strong> We score each machine on <strong>brew quality</strong>, <strong>grinder consistency requirements</strong>, <strong>usability</strong>, <strong>cleaning burden</strong>, and <strong>value for money</strong>. For this cluster, we also weight milk texture quality and first-week beginner friction.</p>

    <h3>Budget-tier winners</h3>
