    <p><strong>Retention/static note:</strong> External grinder quality matters; fine static clumps can amplify channeling risk on compact baskets.</p>
    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It is one of the few truly compact machines that still offers full espresso + milk functionality.</p>

    <h3>5) Flair Neo Flex — Best Manual Espresso Value</h3>
    <p><strong>Verdict:</strong> Best for enthusiasts who want control and better shot potential per dollar than most electric units.</p>
    <p><strong>Buy this if...</strong> you enjoy hands-on brewing and are willing to learn manual pressure control.</p>
    <p><strong>Skip this if...</strong> you need fast back-to-back milk drinks with no prep friction.</p>
