    <p><strong>Key specs:</strong> Semi-auto · 15-bar claim · pressurized basket · steam wand · 37 oz tank · Espresso-capable: Yes.</p>
    <p><strong>Retention/static note:</strong> Better grinder consistency noticeably improves this machine; static-heavy fine grinds can still choke shots.</p>
    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It is one of the most dependable budget pumps for buyers who care about ownership lifespan.</p>
